=No. 1 For You Special Edition=

13
00:00:50,210 --> 00:00:52,450
Do you want to die?

14
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:57,120
You have gastropathy.

15
00:00:57,220 --> 00:00:58,690
Why did you have spicy hotpot?

16
